OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of Valdo Calocane victim won't
OL,4,Cforgive police for viewing attack
OL,5,Cfootage
OL,7,FThe parents of a university student
OL,8,Fwho was killed by paranoid
OL,9,Fschizophrenic Valdo Calocane have said
OL,10,Fthey will "never forgive" the police
OL,11,Fwho accessed footage from the attacks
OL,12,Fand sent WhatsApp messages about their
OL,13,Fson's injuries.
OL,15,FEmma Webber, whose 19-year-old son
OL,16,FBarnaby was killed in the Nottingham
OL,17,Fattacks in June 2023, said a WhatsApp
OL,18,Fmessage sent by a police officer
OL,19,Freferencing the undergraduate's wounds
OL,20,Fis "disgusting and grotesque".
OL,26,@rD@KOUrD@YO]|D@DOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of Valdo Calocane victim won't
OL,4,Cforgive police for viewing attack
OL,5,Cfootage
OL,7,FMr Webber and his friend Grace
OL,8,FO'Malley-Kumar, a first-year medical
OL,9,Fstudent, were killed by Calocane in
OL,10,FIlkeston Road, Nottingham, in the
OL,11,Fearly hours of 13 June 2023, in an
OL,12,Fattack described as "the stuff of
OL,13,Fnightmares".
OL,15,FThe killer then killed caretaker Ian
OL,16,FCoates, 65, before using his van to
OL,17,Frun over three pedestrians.
OL,26,@tD@UOUuD@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of Valdo Calocane victim won't
OL,4,Cforgive police for viewing attack
OL,5,Cfootage
OL,7,FDuring their evidence on Wednesday,
OL,8,Fsat with a picture of Mr Webber on the
OL,9,Fdesk, his parents told the inquiry
OL,10,Fthey were made aware of a WhatsApp
OL,11,Fmessage sent by an officer because the
OL,12,FDaily Mail were intending to publish
OL,13,Fan article about it the next day.
OL,15,FMrs Webber told the inquiry: "Reading
OL,16,Fthe content of that WhatsApp message,
OL,17,Fit was so destructive, so destroying,
OL,18,Fso awful.
OL,26,@wD@^OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of Valdo Calocane victim won't
OL,4,Cforgive police for viewing attack
OL,5,Cfootage
OL,7,F"I don't mind the words being made
OL,8,Fpublic because the author of that
OL,9,Fmessage chose to refer to our children
OL,10,Fas being 'properly butchered' and
OL,11,F'innards out' and everything.
OL,13,F"That's disgusting and grotesque."
OL,15,FThe mother said: "I think there is a
OL,16,Fclear line between gallows humour and
OL,17,Fa very clear need to be able to handle
OL,18,Fwhat is often a very, very difficult
OL,19,Fjob, similarly to the way doctors or
OL,20,Ffire people would. But this steps over
OL,21,Fthat mark."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUuD@bO]wD@ROU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of Valdo Calocane victim won't
OL,4,Cforgive police for viewing attack
OL,5,Cfootage
OL,7,FShe told the inquiry that officers had
OL,8,Fviewed footage of her son "lying on
OL,9,Fthe road, having been brutally stabbed
OL,10,Fmultiple times, fighting for his life
OL,11,Fand ultimately losing it".
OL,13,FShe continued: "And that's wrong,
OL,14,Fthat's so wrong, and I will never
OL,15,Fforgive them. And I hope that they're
OL,16,Flistening to part of this and
OL,17,Frethinking their actions."
OL,26,@pD@[OUsD@YO]uD@POUyD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of Valdo Calocane victim won't
OL,4,Cforgive police for viewing attack
OL,5,Cfootage
OL,7,FDavid Webber, Barnaby's father, said:
OL,8,F"We were told all the way through this
OL,9,F(the investigation) that, for VC
OL,10,F(Valdo Calocane), privacy was
OL,11,Fmassively important.
OL,13,F"And it does seem to me that again, in
OL,14,Fthis case, my son, who was the victim
OL,15,Fhere, his privacy was not taken into
OL,16,Fconsideration.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of Valdo Calocane victim won't
OL,4,Cforgive police for viewing attack
OL,5,Cfootage
OL,7,F"Grace's privacy wasn't taken in
OL,8,Fconsideration. Ian's wasn't taken into
OL,9,Fconsideration. You're thinking 'this
OL,10,Fis wrong, you can't have it both
OL,11,Fways'."
OL,13,FMr Webber said that the police had
OL,14,F"let us down" by how they handled the
OL,15,Fcase.
OL,17,FHe said: "My brother's a police
OL,18,Fofficer, my sister an ex-police
OL,19,Fofficer. I have nothing but respect
OL,20,Ffor the police and have always had
OL,21,Frespect for the police.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@GO]vD@AOUvD@MO]yD@JOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of Valdo Calocane victim won't
OL,4,Cforgive police for viewing attack
OL,5,Cfootage
OL,7,F"However in this particular case, they
OL,8,Fhave fallen very short of what I would
OL,9,Fexpect someone who is there to
OL,10,Feffectively protect the public should
OL,11,Fbe doing."
OL,13,FHe added: "In this case, they have let
OL,14,Fus down. And they have acted in a way
OL,15,Fthat I think is abhorrent.
OL,17,F"I can't forgive them for that because
OL,18,Fthis is my son, again, at the bottom
OL,19,Fof this.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@JO]uD@KOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of Valdo Calocane victim won't
OL,4,Cforgive police for viewing attack
OL,5,Cfootage
OL,7,F"He didn't ask for anything else, you
OL,8,Fknow, he should have been protected by
OL,9,Fthem and they didn't do it."
OL,11,FIn a speech at the end of their
OL,12,Fevidence, Mrs Webber said: "My son was
OL,13,Fmurdered at 19-years-old by a violent,
OL,14,Fpernicious and dangerous 32-year-old
OL,15,Fman allowed to roam the streets and
OL,16,Funleash his planned attacks with his
OL,17,Frucksacks full of weapons and ambush
OL,18,Fthose weaker than himself.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@\O]tD@\OU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,378,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1774555873
OL,3,CParents of Valdo Calocane victim won't
OL,4,Cforgive police for viewing attack
OL,5,Cfootage
OL,7,FShe continued: "It is the stuff of
OL,8,Fnightmares and the true face of evil.
OL,9,FClearly a sick individual, that is
OL,10,Fnever disputed.
OL,12,F"However it is one that knew what he
OL,13,Fwas doing, he knew it was wrong and he
OL,14,Fdid it anyway.
OL,16,F"A master manipulator and a ticking
OL,17,Ftime bomb, a tragedy waiting to
OL,18,Fhappen."
OL,20,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,26,@oD@POUtD@AOUxD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
